data.description: This charming 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence located in the Forster Meadows neighborhood is just a block away from the community park, offering convenience and leisure right at your fingertips.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere. The main floor features a spacious living area, perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing with family. The well-appointed kitchen boasts modern appliances and ample cabinet space, with the refrigerator included as part of the property.  Upstairs, you'll find all three bedrooms, providing privacy and comfort for everyone in the household. The convenient location of the laundry room upstairs adds to the practicality of this home.  Step outside to discover your own private oasis. A covered patio overlooks the expansive yard, offering plenty of space for outdoor gatherings, gardening, or simply enjoying the fresh air.  And let's not forget about the neighborhood amenities! Just a short walk away is the community park, complete with a dog park, pavilion, and playground, providing endless opportunities for recreation and enjoyment.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this wonderful property your own. Schedule a showing today and start envisioning the possibilities of life in this delightful home!
